01:07:36.550 --> 01:07:42.630
relying on Him. Study and meditate in order to strengthen your conviction that Jehovah will take

01:07:42.630 --> 01:07:51.429
care of you. He promises to do so. In all of this, don't forget your past blessings. Just as Jehovah

